 If today is the palindrome day of 2020, then today is 02/02/2020. A month ago from today is 1 month in the past of today, which is the last day of January 2020, or 01/31/2020. So the answer is 01/31/2020.

Q: Today
Answer 01/31/2020 expected 01/02/2020
Total examples: 33 Correct answers: 23
